WEBVTT

00:02:28.875 --> 00:02:33.181
Stress oqibati miyaning DNK qatlamigacha
kirib boradi.

00:02:33.181 --> 00:02:34.497
Eksperiment yangi

00:02:34.497 --> 00:02:38.706
tug'ilgan kalamushning onasi tomonidan 
qancha parvarishlanishi

00:02:38.706 --> 00:02:43.878
kelgusida go’dakning stressga moyilligini 
aniqlashda qo'l kelishini ko’rsatdi.

00:02:43.878 --> 00:02:48.336
G’amxo’r ona farzandlari stress ta’siriga 
kamroq berilar ekan,

00:02:48.336 --> 00:02:51.769
chunki ularning miyasida ko’proq 
kortizol retseptorlari mavjud,

00:02:51.769 --> 00:02:54.757
kortizolni saqlab, 
stressga barham beradi.

00:02:54.757 --> 00:02:58.223
E’tiborsiz ona farzandlarida esa 
buning aksi,

00:02:58.223 --> 00:03:01.910
shu sabab umri davomida stress bilan 
ko’proq to’qnashishadi.